<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1039104" n="1"/> 
  <note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895">Ad eundem.</note>
<opener><lb/><salute>Amice dilecte</salute>.</opener>
  <p><lb/><rs type="lostletter">Literas</rs> tuas humanissimas ante <date>quatriduum</date> scriptas <date>nudius tertius</date> accepi, ex quibus lubens intellexi, ra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tiones solutionis sex florenorum <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me allatas tibi satisfecisse. Thalerum quem <rs type="person">Pedellus</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me etiam exegit
    <lb/>nondum solvi, quia hoc ipsius petitum nimis impudenter fieri, su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>amque nimis magnam esse existima<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bam, quum neminem in specie tuo nomine invitare necesse habuit, nisi quos ex officio omnium Can<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>didatorum nomine invitare debuit, ut Scholarchas, Professores, Pastores, <choice><orig><g ref="#pp">pp.</g></orig><reg>etc.</reg></choice> quare dimidio thalero illum
    <lb/>contentum esse posse judico, quem ipsi ulterius instanti solvam, nisi jam <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>Dnis</abbr> Scholarchis pro
    <lb/>te acceperit florenum, <abbr>Ampl.</abbr> <abbr>n.</abbr> <abbr>Dn.</abbr> <rs type="person">Sch.</rs> singulis Magistris recens promotis florenum pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>mii
    <lb/>loco dant, saltem Basileensibus, et ni fallor etiam extraneis; quod si igitur cognovero hunc flore<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>num etiam extraneis dari, et <rs type="person">Pedellum</rs> illum, qui tibi debetur, dolose retinuisse, ipsi quidem
    <lb/>dictum florenum relinquam, sed ultra hoc nihil amplius <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me consequetur. Memini me etiam,
    <lb/>cum gradum capiebam, <rs type="person">Pedello</rs> florenum meum, quem <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>Dnis</abbr> <rs type="person">Schol.</rs> acceperat, pro invitatione
    <lb/>reliquisse. Gratias tibi ago pro suscepto labore in excerpendo <rs type="biblio">catalogo</rs>, quem mihi misisti, in quo
    <lb/>nihil desidero, nisi quod non fuerit electus annus antiquior <abbr>ex. gr.</abbr> annus 1600<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> aut 1610<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> vel alius
    <lb/>loco annorum 1630 et 1640, scire etenim non possum, quamdiu singuli, qui his annis nati sunt, vi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>xerint, quia quidam eorum adhuc supersunt, ideo <abbr>Dn.</abbr> <rs type="person">Jacobo Zörnlino</rs>, ut monuisti, <rs type="letter">literas</rs> hasce
    <lb/>inclusas scripsi, quibus illum rogo, ut non dedignetur aliquot pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terea annorum <rs type="biblio">catalogum</rs> conficere<supplied>,</supplied>
    <pb facs="1039105" n="2"/>
    <lb/>quid autem h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c tua verba: et ipse <rs type="letter">literis</rs> <hi rend="u">duabus</hi> ab ipso petere poteris; velint, non percipio. Honorari<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>um, de quo scribis, pro labore quem gravem esse facile video, ipsi persolvere, uti par est, non cessabo,
    <lb/>vel tu ipse Dominum <rs type="person">Zörnlium</rs> haud gravate, quod <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> te amic<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> efflagito, pro opera, quam forte jam
    <lb/>in se suscepit vel adhuc suscipiet, meo nomine remuneraberis, quod expenderis lubentissime <abbr>Dno</abbr>
    <lb/><rs type="person">Im Hof</rs> refundam. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum propositum tuum iter in <rs type="place">Palatinatum</rs> felix esse jubeat <abbr>D. O. M.</abbr>
    <lb/>et spiritus sui <choice><abbr>SSti</abbr><expan>Sancti</expan></choice> <foreign xml:lang="grc">χαρίσματα</foreign><note type="editorial">χαρίσματα ist das Plural von χάρισμα; es bedeutet "Gabe der Gnade", "Charisma", "geistliche Gabe".</note> in te augeat, quo Ecclesi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tibi co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>issa est, guberna<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tionem ita possis instituere, ut illa ad altissimi sui nominis gloriam, tuam salutem, et ipsius
    <lb/>Ecclesi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in fide Christiana incrementum cedat longe latissimum! </p><closer><salute>Vale et memori<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> com<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mendatum habe Amicum tuum obsequentissimum</salute> <signed><rs type="person"><rs type="person">NB.</rs></rs></signed></closer>
</div>
</body>
</text></TEI>